<div type="definition">
<p>ADDRESS OTHERS in EXPLAINING SUPERNATURAL TRUTHS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>000</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>說教 is a current word for preaching.</p>
<p>說法 refers literally to the preaching of Buddhism, but is used much more widely.</p>
<p>傳教 has something of a missionary flavour.</p>
<p>傳道 refers generally to the preaching of any tradition.</p>
<p>布道 focusses on the spreading of an intellectual or religious tradition.</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
